  <p id="upgrade-container-deets" class="deets">
    We need the above information to securely pass onto our payment processor Paddle to calculate tax and be compliant.<br>We don't store any of it. Once you click "Upgrade", you'll be presented with a payment box provided by Paddle.com. In case if you're a GDPR-nerd, you can find links to Paddle's terms and conditions and privacy policy in our privacy policy.
  </p>


